{"tid":1786363,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一張圖 JJ插沙求救 #adore","createTime":"2019-12-17T05:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T19:20:19.000Z","uid":17376,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bd626a76c1e9a6f1cada3ce0ecafc4ed0b20149e","tid":1786363,"uid":17376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"Sorry唔知開係咩台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幅圖係上下兩格<br />\n然後上面嗰格係有個人好無助咁坐係度<br />\n背景有超多負面啲字 啲字係英文嚟<br />\n然後下面嗰格係 有個人（好似係女仔）出現左<br />\n撫摸住一開始個人塊面 然後背景得返一個 You. 字<br />\n其他所有字都消失哂 大概係咁<br />\n唔好意思阻到大家 Google左勁耐都搵唔到<br />\n所以想上嚟問一問大家有無呢幅圖係手<br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6092ee75720a70e4092d94e6799d759d6870f9de","tid":1786363,"uid":17376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ff103f13ef3a1a3680ad12c3482c0a1ea4b78e","tid":1786363,"uid":17376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c141cb2526104a6f5a34b5b2ac7203d602a0342","tid":1786363,"uid":17376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /